modName: ALSL Body - CBBE BBP TBBP HDT Bodyslide presets
summary: Realistic looking body, with BBP and TBBP breasts physics and HDT collision support. Wide range of body sizes, from skinny to curvy. Different-looking female NPCs in game.
descriptionHtml:
WARNING! NUDITY! (if you don’t get it yet)


Realistic looking body, with TBBP breasts physics. Wide range of body sizes, from skinny to curvy. Different-looking female NPCs in game.


OVERVIEW:

“ALSL Body” – Minimal weight is skinny with small breasts. Maximum weight is similar to CBBE, but with bigger and more saggy breasts. Most females in game will look average. Not immersion breaking.

“ALSL Curvy Body” - Minimal weight is skinny with small breasts. Maximum weight is curvier, with bigger breasts, than “ALSL Body”. Could be immersion breaking.

“Daedric Revealed Armor for Curvy Body” – check screenshot ;) . Totally immersion breaking.

“TBBP Skeleton” – female skeleton of normal size, with TBBP bones. If you experiences animation glitches (spinning weapon in left hand in TPS mode, clipping into horse while riding) try to use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11811/?]FNIS[/url].


FEATURES:

-Compatible with any CBBE texture packs.

-Compatible with all TBBP and BBP animations.

-HDT physics collision in version 1.2

-Bodyslide preset - easy to change as you want.

-Additional Bodyslide preset with breasts cleavage for armors and clothes.


IMPORTANT NOTES!

Use proper skeleton! I recommend to use [url=https://www.google.com/search?num=100&safe=off&site=&source=hp&q=XP32+Maximum+Skeleton+Extended&oq=XP32+Maximum+Skeleton+Extended&gs_l=hp.3..0l10.2644.2644.0.6000.2.2.0.0.0.0.87.158.2.2.0.msedr...0...1c.2.60.hp..1.1.70.0.NbK6SEVuHB8]XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended[/url]. If you play as ELF or ORC and experience crashes, try to use [url=https://www.google.com/search?num=100&safe=off&q=Orc%26ElfFix4TBBP.esp&oq=Orc%26ElfFix4TBBP.esp&gs_l=serp.3...1329638.1329638.0.1331615.1.1.0.0.0.0.175.175.0j1.1.0.msedr...0...1c.2.60.serp..1.0.0.tyhBdeqUah0]Orc&ElfFix4TBBP.esp[/url].


REQUIRED MODS:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]"Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE-"[/url] by Caliente.


REQUIRED MODS FOR BODYSLIDE 2 PRESETS:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/?]"BodySlide 2 and Outfit Studio"[/url] by Caliente.


REQUIRED MODS FOR BODYSLIDE++ PRESETS:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32731/?]"Bodyslide CB Plus Plus - Extra Sliders for CBBE and Outfits"[/url] by stuffed_bunny - ChronoTrigger77 – ousnius.


REQUIRED MODS FOR HDT PHYSICS:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53996/?]"HDT Physics Extensions"[/url] by HydrogensaysHDT.


RECOMMENDED MODS:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/45453/?]"True Daughters of Skyrim"[/url] by betterbecause.

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54044/?]"HDT Breast And Butt Physics - TBBP BBP Supported"[/url] by threedeedevil. – IF YOU WANT HDT BREASTS COLLISION.


INSTALLATION:

1. Install "Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE-" mod.

2. Install TBBP compatible skeleton.

3. Install this mod with overwriting files.
